Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:29.52,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,雖然在SNS上發帖了  但會有人來麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.36,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:37.99,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我家公寓禁止養寵物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:43.41,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,那個東西  是附在貓身上的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:47.54,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,不過  一定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.13,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,畢竟它那麼可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:51.67,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,哇  好小巧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.63,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,我簡直都想把你給吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:55.59,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,來  咕嚕轉圈圈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.84,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,華  玩得太過了當心…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:17:59.18,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:01.31,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,對  對不…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.15,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:22.33,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.33,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,見子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.16,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,他好像一直在往我們這邊看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.75,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,我會不會被他殺掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:32.29,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,不  那個人應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:37.72,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,打擾了  你們是在找飼主的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:39.63,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:43.06,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,我想領養小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.10,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.64,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,碰巧我就在附近真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:51.48,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,是的  雖說我們發現了這孩子  但也很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:55.15,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,太好了  看起來是很善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:56.28,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.57,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,見子  你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:03.24,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,這個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:15.80,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:28.98,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,貓不能給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:35.52,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:38.74,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.03,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,不  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:42.57,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:47.37,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.75,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.26,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,那個人還在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:06.05,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,我說  見子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:10.10,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,要不我們先離開這  換個地方再尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.27,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,見子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:22.70,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:36.88,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,好  我會好好珍惜它的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:54.90,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:05.20,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,這…這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:07.53,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,應該沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.83,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,不可以貌取人
